fields.title: Description
fields.description:
The Samsung Galaxy A54 5G is a feature-rich smartphone that offers flagship-like experiences at a mid-range price. Released in March 2023, it combines a sleek design, robust performance, and versatile camera capabilities, making it an excellent choice for users seeking quality without compromise.

Stunning Display

Enjoy vibrant visuals on the 6.4-inch FHD+ Super AMOLED display with a 120Hz refresh rate. Whether you're streaming videos, gaming, or browsing, the screen delivers smooth and crisp imagery, even under direct sunlight .

fields.title: Additional Info
fields.description:
Versatile Camera System

Capture life's moments with the 50MP main camera, complemented by a 12MP ultra-wide lens and a 5MP macro sensor. The camera setup supports 4K video recording and features Optical Image Stabilization (OIS) and Video Digital Image Stabilization (VDIS), ensuring steady and clear footage .The SunSamsung

All-Day Battery Life

Powered by a 5,000mAh battery, the Galaxy A54 5G offers up to two days of usage on a single charge, depending on individual usage patterns. Fast charging capabilities ensure you're back up and running quickly .The Sun

Robust Performance

Equipped with the Exynos 1380 processor and options for 6GB or 8GB RAM, the Galaxy A54 5G handles multitasking and demanding applications with ease. Paired with One UI based on Android 13, the device provides a smooth and intuitive user experience .

5G Connectivity

Stay connected with 5G support, ensuring fast download and upload speeds, seamless streaming, and smooth online gaming experiences.
